title: Elemental (music group)
text:
Elemental is a hip-hop group from Zagreb, Croatia, founded in 1998. By Luka Tralić Shot, Gordan Radočaj Ink and Mirela Priselac Remi, one of Croatia's few female rappers.


== Awards ==
